msgid ""
"The default branch for this project has been changed. Please update your bookm"
"arks."
msgstr "此项目的默认分支已更改。请更新您的书签。"

msgid ""
"MemberRole|The None role is assigned to the invited group users of a shared pr"
"oject when project sharing is disabled in group setting."
msgstr "当群组设置中禁用项目共享时，\"无\"角色将分配给共享项目的受邀群组用户。"

msgid ""
"MemberRole|The Guest role is for users who need visibility into a project or g"
"roup but should not have the ability to make changes, such as external stakeho"
"lders."
msgstr "访客角色适用于需要查看项目或群组但不应进行更改的用户，例如外部利益相关者。"

msgid ""
"MemberRole|The Planner role is suitable for team members who need to manage pr"
"ojects and track work items but do not need to contribute code."
msgstr "规划者角色适合需要管理项目和跟踪工作项但无需贡献代码的团队成员。"

msgid ""
"MemberRole|The Reporter role is suitable for team members who need to stay inf"
"ormed about a project or group but do not actively contribute code."
msgstr "报告者角色适合需要了解项目或群组动态但不积极贡献代码的团队成员。"

msgid ""
"MemberRole|The Security Manager role is for security team members who need to "
"view and manage security features for the group or project."
msgstr "安全管理员角色适用于需要查看和管理群组或项目安全功能的安全团队成员。"

msgid ""
"MemberRole|The Developer role gives users access to contribute code while rest"
"ricting sensitive administrative actions."
msgstr "开发者角色允许用户贡献代码，同时限制敏感的管理操作。"

msgid ""
"MemberRole|The Maintainer role is primarily used for managing code reviews, ap"
"provals, and administrative settings for projects. This role can also manage p"
"roject memberships."
msgstr "维护者角色主要用于管理代码审查、审批及项目管理设置，也可管理项目成员资格。"

msgid ""
"MemberRole|The Owner role is typically assigned to the individual or team resp"
"onsible for managing and maintaining the group or creating the project. This r"
"ole has the highest level of administrative control, and can manage all aspect"
"s of the group or project, including managing other Owners."
msgstr "所有者角色通常分配给负责管理和维护群组或创建项目的个人或团队。此角色具有最高级别的管理权限，可管理群组或项目的所有方面，包括管理其他所有者。"

msgid "DefaultBranchProtection|Not protected"
msgstr "不受保护"

msgid ""
"DefaultBranchProtection|Both developers and maintainers can push new commits, "
"force push, or delete the branch."
msgstr "开发者和维护者均可推送新提交、强制推送或删除分支。"

msgid "DefaultBranchProtection|Protected against pushes"
msgstr "防止推送保护"

msgid ""
"DefaultBranchProtection|Developers cannot push new commits, but are allowed to"
" accept merge requests to the branch. Maintainers can push to the branch."
msgstr "开发者无法推送新提交，但允许接受合并请求到该分支。维护者可以推送到该分支。"

msgid "DefaultBranchProtection|Partially protected"
msgstr "部分保护"

msgid ""
"DefaultBranchProtection|Both developers and maintainers can push new commits, "
"but cannot force push."
msgstr "开发者和维护者均可推送新提交，但不能强制推送。"

msgid "DefaultBranchProtection|Fully protected"
msgstr "完全保护"

msgid ""
"DefaultBranchProtection|Developers cannot push new commits, but maintainers ca"
"n. No one can force push."
msgstr "开发者无法推送新提交，但维护者可以。任何人均不能强制推送。"

msgid "DefaultBranchProtection|Fully protected after initial push"
msgstr "初次推送后完全保护"

msgid ""
"DefaultBranchProtection|Developers can push the initial commit to a repository"
", but none afterward. Maintainers can always push. No one can force push."
msgstr "开发者可以推送初始提交到仓库，但之后不能。维护者始终可以推送。任何人均不能强制推送。"

msgid "DefaultBranchProtection|Protected"
msgstr "受保护"

msgid ""
"DefaultBranchProtection|Once a repository is created this branch will be prote"
"cted."
msgstr "仓库创建后，此分支将受到保护。"

